1. *Šansa* da će biti izabran je minorna. (The chance of being chosen is minor.)
2. *Šansu* da ostaneš udobno smo svi želeli. (We all wanted the chance to stay comfortable.)
3. *Šansi* da napraviš grešku je sada manje. (The chance to make a mistake is now less.)
4. *Šansama* da postaneš bolji sreća se smeje. (Luck laughs at the chances of becoming better.)
5. *Šansu* da se nešto promeni postoji. (There is a chance for something to change.)